                <item xml:id="addition1" n="1">
                  <label>Colophon</label>
                  <locus from="166b"/>
                  <p>The colophon, fol. 166 b, belongs to the time when the manuscript was repaired, and foll. 106 and 166 added to it. It states that the book was the property of certain persons, whose names have been erased (that of <persName ref="smblPers824">Hannān of <placeName ref="http://syriaca.org/place/193">Tagrīt</placeName>
                    </persName> being substituted), and that it was bound by one <persName ref="smblPers">Iyār</persName>.</p>
                  <p>
