                  <p>Another reader has written on the margin <foreign xml:lang="syr">ܒܢܝܫܐ ܕܡܪܝ ܐܦܪܝܡ ܐܬܚܫܚ</foreign>, "he has used the metre of <persName>Mār Ephraim</persName>."</p>
